# Idea Parking Lot
### *Future projects, half-formed thoughts, things worth revisiting*
### *BOB monitors this file. You own it.*

> **This is a TEMPLATE.** Copy this file to `IDEA_PARKING_LOT.md` and use it as your personal idea queue. The real `IDEA_PARKING_LOT.md` is gitignored so it never leaks to the public repo.

---

> **How this works:** Drop ideas here in any state — rough, half-baked, or fully formed.
> Nothing in this file is a commitment. It's a holding pen.
> BOB reviews it during project planning and flags anything worth activating.
> You make all final calls on what moves from here to `MISSION.md`.

